latestPosts.caption:
In a world softened by Paris filters, i chose to be Raw and Real.
Sharing this close-up, filter-free video of my bridal makeup to show the reality of makeup. If you have textured skin, pores, or fine lines — you’ll still have them after makeup. Makeup enhances, not erases. Only filters or procedures like Botox or fillers can truly blur skin texture. This is real skin, real makeup, and I believe in showing you the truth, not the illusion.
